  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Internal communications</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Internal communications to enhance internal understanding of our way of working, mission, and vision is crucial to achieve our Network&#x2019;s goals, and will receive high attention as well. Communications and Campaigns team members act as communications advisors to other teams in Solidaridad Europe, leading to higher levels of communications and better aligned communication activities. We will facilitate, align and streamline information needs within Solidaridad Europe, by developing the intranet, and organizing internal meetings.

Various communication tools, including social media, parts of our website, powerpoints, printed material and videos, will be renewed and staff will be trained in the use and share of these tools, and will be motivated to increase visibility within their networks, mostly via social media and events. New internal sites have been set up for knowledge sharing and existing sites have been updated and improved. Also, a start was made with internal webinars around more technical topics by technical experts, for example on how to use internal tools.</narrative>
  </description>
